if xfee = [01]
   y1 = val(substr(dtoc(l_fdate),1,2))
   ymo = xmo1 [y1]
   l_fmonth = xmo1 [y1]

   * --12.07.10: implement proration for passenger plate renewal

   * prorate only original plate
